description:
Feel free to learn from, remix, or copy any of my mod parts. 
Just want to use the parts? Subscribe!
Learning to script but can't model? Feel free to use one!
Want to make your own model but not rewrite the functionality of one of my parts? Use the script!
Don't know how to mod but want to copy paste just the parts you want into your own special blend? Go for it!
Just looking for how I did something? Feel free to poke around, but I've been learning LUA and the Scrap Mechanic API as I go, so my solutions may not be the best solutions.
name: MJM Mod
